                    <div class="tmm-sitcky1-item_title">
                      <div
                        class="tmm-text-size-large tmm-text-weight-semibold"
                      >
                        John Doe
                      </div>
                      <div
                        class="tmm-text-size-medium tmm-sticky1-item-content_middle"
                      >
                        CEO
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p>John is a visionary leader with a passion for driving innovation and growth.</p>
